shadow_expressions.description: Unconscious or imbalanced manifestations of Sun energy

insights.insight: In Sun's sacred space morning activation, the Sun consciousness shadow creates excessive self-focus—making everything about you rather than recognizing your role in the larger cosmic dance.
In Sun's sacred space morning activation, the Sun consciousness shadow manifests as ego inflation—believing you're superior to others rather than recognizing your unique but equal divine nature.
This morning's Sun energy field reveals that the Sun consciousness shadow creates attention seeking—craving external validation rather than developing genuine self-worth and authentic contribution.
This morning's Sun energy field reveals that the Sun consciousness shadow manifests as domination—controlling others to feel powerful rather than inspiring them to discover their own strength.
